OL,4,CRuth Madeley: Actress says taxi driver
OL,5,Ctook her wheelchair away
OL,6, Actress Ruth Madeley has revealed a
OL,7, taxi driver took her wheelchair away
OL,8, following an argument after refusing to
OL,9, drive her to an accessible entrance.
OL,11,FPosting about the incident at London's
OL,12,FEuston train station last month,
OL,13,FBafta-nominated Madeley said the driver
OL,14,Fbelieved that because he'd seen her
OL,15,Fstand, he "knew (she) could walk".
OL,17,FShe added the driver then demanded an
OL,18,Fextra fee and took her wheelchair away.
OL,20,FTransport for London has apologised for
OL,21,Fthe "utterly appalling" incident.
